# Nebula CLI - Tab Navigation
Output out.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set FontSize 14

Type "nebula"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "2"
Sleep 500ms
Type "3"
Sleep 500ms
Type "4"
Sleep 500ms
Type "5"
Sleep 500ms
Type "6"
Sleep 500ms
Type "7"
Sleep 500ms
Type "8"
Sleep 500ms
Type "9"
Sleep 500ms
Type "0"
Sleep 500ms
Type "1"
Sleep 500ms
